reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Teen dream set!
reviews.reviewText: My daughter, who is 16 years old, got this for Christmas and loves it! She loves all things makeup, but this was such a complete set that she's slightly obsessed with trying it all out and making sure she got the perfect look before going back to school. I like that it's fairly compact and has it's own carrying bag to make it easier for her to pick up and work on her organizational skills. Great gift for a teen!
